  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_16_4",
    "text": "小青蛙说：“荷叶是我的歌台。”小青蛙蹲在荷叶上，呱呱地放声歌唱。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
